title: Terrace - means an open-to-sky flat roof of a building or part of a building, provided with a parapet for safety and with or without any cantilevered portion
clause_text: Terrace - means an open-to-sky flat roof of a building or part of a building, provided with a parapet for safety and with or without any cantilevered portion.
